data.description: Must See! Beautifully updated brick home with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  This lovely home has had many updates and comes with plenty of space.  3 car covered parking.  Nice sized closets in all bedrooms, huge master bedroom with walk in closet, large kitchen with plenty of counter space and cabinets.  Very nicely updated bathrooms with large privacy fenced back yard.  The back yard features 2 decks on back, a tiny one bed one bath home heated and cooled with a mini split, storm shelter and storage building. There is a lot to love about this move in ready home.  Schedule your appointment today!
